Package: capacc
Type: Package
Title: Collective and point anomalies in cross-correlated data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Martin Tveten
Maintainer: Martin Tveten <matveten@gmail.com>
Description: An efficient implementation of the CAPA-CC method and CPT-CC for a single change.
    Includes plotting functionality from the anomaly package, as well as code for reproducing results in the paper Tveten, Eckley, Fearnhead (2020) "Scalable changepoint and anaomly detection in cross-correlated data with an application to condition monitoring".
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
